    <abstract>
      <t>   This document describes how to specify SM2 Digital Signature
   Algorithm keys and signatures in DNS Security (DNSSEC).  It lists the
   curve and uses SM3 as hash algorithm for signatures.

   This draft is an independent submission to the RFC series, and does
   not have consensus of the IETF community.

